description: We are here to bring you a wonderfully new, and diverse twist to traditional MIddle Eastern / Mediterranean food.  We specialize in Falafel but also have an other non-vegetarian Mediterranean, street food staples. >In case you wondering: Falafels balls are a wonderful mesh of grounded garbanzo beans, various veggies, and spices. Fried to create a delicious crunchy outer shell. The balls are in then placed in a made fresh daily bread pocket with your combination choice of vegetables, pickled veggies, and dressings.All falafel sandwiches are 100% vegatarian, and 100% delicious!Our standard truck menu is posted here on Roaming hunger but other options are available upon request.  We can cater to all vegetarian crowds and we can also mix it up, catering to the non-vegetarians as well.
name: Yalla Truck
